      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        568.21,
        472.54,
        577.21
      ],
      "text": "alleen, doelen wij op brieven, e-mails inclusief bijlagen, sms'jes en WhatsApp-berichten.",
